  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No rigid classes</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/a91602ba3be23381df449bc74cb71429.poster.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/a91602ba3be23381df449bc74cb71429.webm?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/a91602ba3be23381df449bc74cb71429.mp4?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can create <strong>your own class</strong>, nothing is locked, feel free to play as a fire mage wielding a two handed sword or a necro archer.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tons of masteries and skills</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/7820c9c47664aaf8640f05bbd129cbae.poster.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/7820c9c47664aaf8640f05bbd129cbae.webm?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/7820c9c47664aaf8640f05bbd129cbae.mp4?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There is a vast number of options to choose from when it comes to spells, weapons, abilities and masteries. You can create a ton of builds and constantly find new ways of crushing your enemies!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Old school action RPG hack and slash with skill based combat.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/05cfbfbf3d4715ec818cc926e9ed8892.poster.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/05cfbfbf3d4715ec818cc926e9ed8892.webm?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/05cfbfbf3d4715ec818cc926e9ed8892.mp4?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Stats are important, but so is evading enemy attacks and aiming yours!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Open world full of quests</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/d7931498d0542415c8b5be5f254056cd.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>Explore the world of Powerlust, travel between cities, find amazing treasures, help npcs find their lost teeth and more!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Made by one guy</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/f153c4b3ed043306b0ed99b88f2e7069.poster.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/f153c4b3ed043306b0ed99b88f2e7069.webm?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/f153c4b3ed043306b0ed99b88f2e7069.mp4?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Hobby project made by one guy (me). I spent quite a few years on it already. No huge corporations involved :)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fun camera mods</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/dfb6948ee7609ccf85138b6401cb0910.poster.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/dfb6948ee7609ccf85138b6401cb0910.webm?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/dfb6948ee7609ccf85138b6401cb0910.mp4?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose the way you play between Isometric, Top Down, TPP and FPP camera modes! Use fun camera filters to make the game look unique.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >I'd love to hear your feedback</h2>I'm still working on this game. I'd appreciate any feedback, it will be a really huge help in further development. Check out my twitter for constant updates and share your thoughts via email or <strong>discord</strong>!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Procedurally generated dungeons.       <br></li><li>Skill-based combat.       <br></li><li>No rigid classes.       <br></li><li>Tons of masteries, items, skills and builds.       <br></li><li>Open world to explore.       <br></li><li>Optional permadeath.       <br></li><li>Controller support.     <br></li><li>Awesome discord community.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >No rigid classes</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/a91602ba3be23381df449bc74cb71429.poster.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/a91602ba3be23381df449bc74cb71429.webm?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/a91602ba3be23381df449bc74cb71429.mp4?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You can create <strong>your own class</strong>, nothing is locked, feel free to play as a fire mage wielding a two handed sword or a necro archer.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tons of masteries and skills</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/7820c9c47664aaf8640f05bbd129cbae.poster.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/7820c9c47664aaf8640f05bbd129cbae.webm?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/7820c9c47664aaf8640f05bbd129cbae.mp4?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>There is a vast number of options to choose from when it comes to spells, weapons, abilities and masteries. You can create a ton of builds and constantly find new ways of crushing your enemies!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Old school action RPG hack and slash with skill based combat.</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/05cfbfbf3d4715ec818cc926e9ed8892.poster.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/05cfbfbf3d4715ec818cc926e9ed8892.webm?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/05cfbfbf3d4715ec818cc926e9ed8892.mp4?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Stats are important, but so is evading enemy attacks and aiming yours!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Open world full of quests</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/d7931498d0542415c8b5be5f254056cd.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 /></span><br>Explore the world of Powerlust, travel between cities, find amazing treasures, help npcs find their lost teeth and more!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Made by one guy</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/f153c4b3ed043306b0ed99b88f2e7069.poster.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/f153c4b3ed043306b0ed99b88f2e7069.webm?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/f153c4b3ed043306b0ed99b88f2e7069.mp4?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Hobby project made by one guy (me). I spent quite a few years on it already. No huge corporations involved :)<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fun camera mods</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/dfb6948ee7609ccf85138b6401cb0910.poster.avif?t=1753956459\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/dfb6948ee7609ccf85138b6401cb0910.webm?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1829520/extras/dfb6948ee7609ccf85138b6401cb0910.mp4?t=1753956459\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose the way you play between Isometric, Top Down, TPP and FPP camera modes! Use fun camera filters to make the game look unique.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >I'd love to hear your feedback</h2>I'm still working on this game. I'd appreciate any feedback, it will be a really huge help in further development. Check out my twitter for constant updates and share your thoughts via email or <strong>discord</strong>!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Procedurally generated dungeons.       <br></li><li>Skill-based combat.       <br></li><li>No rigid classes.       <br></li><li>Tons of masteries, items, skills and builds.       <br></li><li>Open world to explore.       <br></li><li>Optional permadeath.       <br></li><li>Controller support.     <br></li><li>Awesome discord community.</li></ul>",
